  <brief_title>S-1 and Irinotecan Combination Chemotherapy for Advanced Gastric Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II Study of S-1 and Irinotecan Combination Chemotherapy in Patients With Advanced Gastric Cancer as a First-Line Therapy</official_title>
