  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary goal of this phase II trial is to evaluate the response rate of combination
      chemotherapy with S-1 and Irinotecan in patients with advanced gastric cancer as a first-line
      therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
